{"tid":1468783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講撚到尾 班死鬼佬咪又係因為跌錢先咁撚興 唔係好似平時咁舉哂手指叫示威者繼續啦","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T14:25:32.000Z","uid":252492,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"883339da8aaff59081bc8560ae56b4598b2a48bc","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:53:06.000Z","msg":"無取消照飛 但佢地入唔到閘<br />\n保險同航空公司都唔賠 班機開撚走左緊係興到火屎啦<br />\n臨時臨急買過張機票成萬銀呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045d3b06b5bc7df6abad9e6a3ecc6682d5f17022","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c23d0d6e4edf2b7cc8f4870d3e3926584bffa5d","tid":1468783,"uid":197393,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:57:46.000Z","msg":"即係同班返工港豬一樣<br />\n<br />\n我哋支持你哋，加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇搞錯呀，示威唔係咁㗎嘛，我哋要返工㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fbd845ff8e38738b7b6abbcb80a51cfd342e13","tid":1468783,"uid":28831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:58:36.000Z","msg":"哇屌<br />\n第一次聽呢個論調<br />\n簡單係真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb5827202bb311f11a1af62dcb985c732096534","tid":1468783,"uid":266203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:00:19.000Z","msg":"個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">文宣道歉日，希望保護過家園的你地明白我們的困境。<br />\n已包埋內地嘅示威活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNcr1bW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNcr1bW.jpg&h=2fdc1bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借多個位<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVtrfTe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVtrfTe.jpg&h=32eb9a6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BNJVTES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBNJVTES.jpg&h=070ec636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SuBgC6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSuBgC6v.jpg&h=4e21a231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EesWC6u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEesWC6u.jpg&h=4d3f45a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZumsKMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZumsKMJ.jpg&h=27bef57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAFM0j4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAFM0j4.jpg&h=40332d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/skJSbrL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FskJSbrL.jpg&h=64f74bb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">free to print : <a href=\"https://we.tl/t-zTHYn0SbVd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwe.tl%2Ft-zTHYn0SbVd&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=e93d03e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://we.tl/t-zTHYn0SbVd</a></span>"},{"pid":"bf3b7751e711563449d24c196e654e5735c04023","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe4ff9d787d93ada8ba197ba074ebba22502071","tid":1468783,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕不割蓆，唯要改進</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n813 之事其實情有可原，因為比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲，我地大家絕對唔會割蓆，但我地亦都要持續去改進，希望運動可以更上一層樓邁向成功之日，我地要一齊尊重，正如人人平等冇話邊個大啲有得話事啲，有咩提議大家投票決定，呢個亦係民主真諦，我地亦要每日一齊去檢討得失，正如人人都會有失誤嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n古今中外所以社會運動總會有失誤嘅時候，呢個係好自然亦可常見嘅事，可貴之處就係識得自省，至少我覺得813 呢日明顯唔係end game 嘅一日，如果有朝一日真係end game 嘅係一戰竟全功嘅時候咁到時我地做乜嘢都可以，但喺呢一日來臨之前嘅過程上，我地唔可以急，仇恨係要記住因為係一股動力，但亦要避免比仇恨支配行動，古今歷史上每一場運動係要好長時日去完成，而且過程係一定會出現爭拗，除咗不割蓆不分化，自省改進，檢討得失，去改善下一步行動亦係成功之道。<br />\n<br />\n已經發生咗嘅事我地冇辦法再去改變，比人射爆隻眼真係好嬲所以我地亦冇資格去怪責甚至割蓆，但我好希望呢場運動可以成功，而呢場運動其中一樣重要嘅係自己要有一個自省精神，一旦出現失誤就要反省，反省完就要檢討，吸取教訓，下次再可以做好啲，人數亦會keep住多，人多就可以贏，如果出現失誤唔去檢討，唔尊重對方互相指罵，只會不斷重複失誤，人數會變少，最後重演2014年雨革失敗歷史。<br />\n<br />\n完美係一種永遠唔會達到但可以追求嘅哲學，所以我地只有不斷改善自己，互相指正，幫大家補鑊，一齊進步，一齊向成功之日進發，煲底之日我地仲要一齊慶祝"},{"pid":"68442077525c4672d973ed8721195eb384f2113c","tid":1468783,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T21:03:36.000Z","msg":"唔好對所有鬼佬有幻想<br />\n咪又係一樣米百樣人"},{"pid":"b4fd3381587e19429d005d7d4ea3e616993b7cc5","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd65ce0f2e738c78fde9363b6be7c3eea1878c6c","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a253167468403e30c77fc8261bfe16c29b5270d2","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6c1da686538089fdef1623de7c7d58da0a4571","tid":1468783,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:49:23.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，停手呀，失民意啦失民意啦，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n民意燃真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效得黎，<br />\n而又乜人都影響唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話民意完全無用，<br />\n一黎民意早已經歸曬邊唔會轉，中立花生友要黎都廢，<br />\n二黎香港又唔係民主政府，幾時聽過民意，<br />\n民意燃仲想攬住民意過世? <br />\n文宣到有700萬人一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫手打政府? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人救過死左好多人嘅烏克蘭、蘇丹、新疆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋有民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n唔好本末倒置，因為民意勒索而乜都唔敢做，<br />\n各有各做，出核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"5b7953703d506e9da5241d19fb4734bdc9be139c","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fdd89aa6a9ee618f052be0eeed8bab6334db75","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdc8af4cda5a8904679d0bbb427382b8c7afcf79","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:38:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749bcbe03aabe5de632f192820b2be34f23ffddb","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46fe990f13e20a4a7f611a98970ad01c47f4255","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47d38abcaade9ca7ae070ce10ccc1fdaa0fe8805","tid":1468783,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0d644fe4af1ee5fbd141e7bca6945552891411","tid":1468783,"uid":25